i Kapoor]], [[Amitabh Bachchan]], [[Vinod Khanna]], [[Shabana Azmi]], [[Neetu Singh]], [[Amjad Khan (actor)|Amjad Khan]], [[Kader Khan]] || Drama ||\n|-\n| ''[[Phir Janam Lenge Hum]]'' || || || || \n|-\n| ''[[Pratima Aur Paayal]]'' || || || || \n|-\n| ''[[Prayashchit]]'' || || || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Priyatama]]'' || [[Basu Chaterjee]] || [[Jeetendra]], [[Neetu Singh]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Ram Bharose]]'' || || [[Randhir Kapoor]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Safed Jhoot]]'' || || [[Vinod Mehra]], [[Moushumi Chatterjee]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Saheb Bahadur]]'' || [[Chetan Anand (director)|Chetan Anand]] || || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Shankar Hussain]]'' || || [[Kanwaljit Singh (actor)|Kanwaljit Singh]] || ||\n|-\n|''[[Shatranj Ke Khiladi (film)|Shatranj Ke Khiladi]]'' || [[Satyajit Ray]] || [[Sanjeev Kumar]], [[Shabana Azmi]], [[Farida Jalal]] || Drama ||\n|-\n| ''[[Shirdi Ke Sai Baba]]'' || || || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Shri Ram Vanvas]]'' || || || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Swami (1977 film)|Swami]]'' || || [[Girish Karnad]], [[Shabana Azmi]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Taxi Taxie]]'' || || [[Amol Palekar]], [[Rama Vij]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Thief of Baghdad (1977 film)|Thief of Baghdad]]'' || || || || \n|-  \n| ''[[Tinku (film)|Tinku]]'' || || [[Rajesh Khanna]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Tyaag]]'' || || [[Rajesh Khanna]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Vishwasghaat (1977 film)|Vishwasghaat]]'' || || [[Sanjeev Kumar]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Yaaron Ka Yaar]]'' || || || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Yehi Hai Zindagi]]'' || || [[Sanjeev Kumar]], [[Lucky Ali]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Zamaanat]]'' || || [[Jeetendra]], [[Reena Roy]], [[Amjad Khan (actor)|Amjad Khan]] || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Zehreeli]]'' || || || ||\n|-\n|}\n{{Indianfilmlist}}\n{{1977 films}}\n{{Filmsbycountry}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://chandrakantha.com/articles/indian_music/filmi_sangeet/film_song_1977.html Indian Film Songs from the Year 1977] - A look back at 1977 with a focus on the Hindi film song\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bollywood Films Of 1977}}\n[[Category:Lists of Bollywood films by year|1977]]\n[[Ca